reviews.review_text: We tried fish burger + fries and crispy garlic chicken wrap and the food did not disappoint. The fish burger was so fresh and tasty, fries are home made and not salty, chicken wrap is full of flavor with lots of veggie and the hummus is seriously the best Ive had. Highly recommend and will definitely come back to try more food. I dont like food that is too salty and the food here is just right!
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Appreciate the support, Kim! Hope to see you again soon! :)

reviews.review_text: I would say the Angry Fish sandwich is a must-order if you can bear with the heat. Its a completely new combination of flavors that amazed me. The pita chips with the spicy hummus dip are also good.
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Thats one fish not mess with! Glad you loved it!

reviews.review_text: The portions are huge and their price is very generous for the amount of food you receive. Not only the quantity but the taste is amazing. I got the Cali Chicken Wrap, and I can definitely see myself coming back here yo eat again in the near future.
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Wow, glad you loved it! Theres plenty more to try on the menu! :) Thank you for your support!

reviews.review_text: My brother recommended this place, so we decided to go for lunch. The restaurant is very clean, the service was quick and the staff was very friendly. We tired the fish burger (with cheese bun) and double cheese burger for mains. They were amazingly delicious. We had the cheese cake and ice cream for dessert. Both of them were mouth watering flavourful . We would highly recommend this place.
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Thanks for sharing! Appreciate your support!

reviews.review_text: ChefHyve is a fantastic restaurant that truly stands out. Their food is not only incredibly fresh but also bursting with flavor. From the first bite, you can tell that they prioritize quality ingredients and expert culinary skills. The menu is diverse, offering a wide range of options to satisfy various tastes.
reviews.response_from_owner_text: So glad to see you appreciate the real ingredients and love we put in making our food! Thanks for sharing! :)

reviews.review_text: New favourite place.  I got 3 takeout chicken plates for dinner.  The 1 chicken feast and 2 Cajun s were both amazing. Great mix of rich flavours and textures in both. Portions are good size, if not on the large side.   Everything was fresh and made there.  The fries didn t make it home they were amazing. Also had a take out cheesecake, outstanding.  Will definitely be back to try other menu items.
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Appreciate the support, thank you! :)

reviews.review_text: Really cute and clean spot. Limited space to sit and wait inside for your food. It took about 25 mins to get my food after ordering inside. The food itself was delicious and I will definitely be coming back here if I m in the area. I ordered the fish sandwich & my boyfriend had the cheeseburger. We also got  free fish bites and fries because of this buy one get one free deal they had when I came in.
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Hey Fernanda! Thats great to hear! Glad you loved the space and the food! Hey, heres a pro tip: You can save time by ordering online at chefhyve.ca. Thanks!

reviews.review_text: I saw this place for the first time last night when I was walking down Kingsway. It looked like they knew what they were doing so I made a note to check it out. I ordered lunch today - the online order process was easy and straightforward. The food was ready according to the time displayed on the website. And the food was EXCELLENT! I had the chicken sandwich with medium spice and coleslaw, with a side of fries and tartar sauce. The bun, chicken, and coleslaw were amazing. The fries  outstanding! I think they season them with paprika. I hope that everyone tries this place out because it s great. I moved back to Vancouver in the spring and I d say that this is the best meal I ve had. Edit: 9 hours later Lunch was so good that I got take-out for dinner. My wife ordered the Chicken Feast and I had the beef street wrap. LIKE WOAH. Everything was amazing, and the prices suspiciously low :) There were only two staff behind the counter on a busy Saturday night so I felt bad for them,  but they were keeping up and the quality of the food is top notch. Also, the cheesecake is sublime.

Great food + service! A bit small and hard to dine in with a group of friends, but otherwise the food is amazing! Unique + perfect if you like a heartier taste. Their fish and chips are definitely a must have.
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Thank you for the kind review, Tracy! Glad you loved the fish & chips! We pride ourselves on having the lightest, crunchiest fish & chips in town! :)

reviews.review_text: I love this place for lunch! Ive only gotten take out but their food is always fresh and in big portions. Dont miss out on their fish and chips, burritos, and wraps. They even season the outside of the burrito! Love the attention to detail in their food.
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Thank you for your continued support! Love the positive vibes!

reviews.review_text: The cali chicken wrap is amazingly delicious with a large amount of chicken and veggies. The fries are also tasty! The server is friendly and eager to answer questions. I would definitely visit again and try more food here! Food
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Thanks, Reese! Would highly recommend the Crunchy Garlic Chicken Wrap as well. Its been a crowd favourite since the start. Appreciate the support! :)

reviews.review_text: Great hidden gem in Vancouver. Ordered the crunchy garlic chicken wrap and it was delicious! The wrap was almost the size of my forearm, so at around $16, it was great value. They have lots of variety but I havent tried anything else yet. Very nice staff, clean restaurant, and great atmosphere. Would recommend.
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Thank you, Gerald! Yes, we make sure you get your moneys worth! :)))

reviews.review_text: Hidden gem! Burrito was the best I ever had, and the food is all very fresh. My friend got the fish/chips and said it was really good also. Staff were nice and prices are awesome. Would definitely go again
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Thats awesome! Thank you for your feedback and support! :)

reviews.review_text: Amazing authentic burgers and desserts. Owner is super friendly as well. Truly a hidden gem of Vancouver. Succulent delicious juicy beef patties. The cheesecake desserts are to die for as well. Everything is super fresh. Have gone back multiple times and will continue to do so. Money extremely well spent.
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Whoa, thats humbling to hear! Thank you! :)

reviews.review_text: First time trying out their food. I ordered fish bites, harvest salad, and chicken feast. Fish bites, fries and salad are fresh and delicious  . I ll come back for their fish and chips and try their desserts next time. ( they have waffles and cheesecakes ! ) The store is super clean and organized Updated: their crunchy chicken with garlic sauce is delicious and the portion is generous. See photos
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Thank you for the support! :) Confident youll enjoy the desserts as well!

reviews.review_text: Chefhyve is the hidden gem that nobody knows about. Hidden on the corner of Slocan and Kingsway, chefhyve offers a variety of fresh menu items which include vegetarian options. The french fries are, hands down, the best french fries in the city.  They remind me of french fries back home in Montreal. The fish burger is so fresh, it quite literally disintegrates into heaven in your mouth.  And just when you think it cant get any better, the wraps are fully loaded with fresh, homemade ingredients, including the wide selection of homemade sauces. I recommend the spicy garlic. If you have a sweet tooth, the make your own ice cream bar lets you create an ice cream bar like no other.  From skor pieces to edible flowers.  Highly instagram-able and equally delicious. To top it all off, I always have a positive experience with the friendly staff.  I had the pleasure of being served by Alex and Daria tonight which prompted me to write this review. Chefhyve makes you feel like you are visiting friends as opposed to just being a client in a restaurant. If you havent tried Chefhyve yet, you are missing out on something special and local in Vancouver.
reviews.response_from_owner_text: We sincerely appreciate your visit and feedback and hope to consistently exceed your expectations! Many thanks for your support!

reviews.review_text: The food is amazing; the burrito and the cheeseburger are outstanding. The cheesecake as week. We tried both the coffee and Lotus flavour. The Lotus cheesecake is a must try :)

My first time impressions of this place are way up there. With one bite into burrito I knew they made a mean burrito.I enjoyed the atmosphere of the place. It is very low key which I like a lot. I hope this place gets the recognition it deserves. Ill definitely come back and try the rest of the menu.
reviews.response_from_owner_text: We hope so too! Look forward to seeing you again!

reviews.review_text: This little jem is just round the corner from us and we love it! Good sized portions, great flavours and really fresh food. Loved the fries and the chicken wrap. Really want to try the fish sandwich. Also the people were so friendly and chatted with us for ages. Highly recommended.
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Thank you, it was our pleasure! Appreciate the support!

reviews.review_text: the owner came in and treated me like a king. made my day. He hooked us up with 2 for 1 Fries and fish Bites.
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Absolutely~! Thats the way it should be! Thanks= you for supporting us! :)

reviews.review_text: This place is amazing! A friend told me about it when he discovered it on uber eats. Went here in person and they have the best food! I love the harvest salad, cheeseburger, custom ice cream bars!!! Yes, custom ice cream bars!!! The owner here has so much pride in his shop, the quality is always top notch and delicious and fresh!!! You must try the custom ice cream bar!!
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Thank you, Liz!! Its a pleasure to serve you, always! :)

reviews.review_text: I got the fish and chips and they were the best I ve had in Vancouver to date, the battered fish in particular is so good it keeps its crunch and is not overly greasy.  Their homemade tartar sauce? 10/10. The venue is small so it s best enjoyed as take out (in my opinion). I will definitely be back to check out the rest of the menu.
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Hey Ryan, Yes, we like to think we have the lightest and crunchiest fish and chips in town! And, yes, we do have a large menu, packed with nothing but crowd favourites! Appreciate the support!

reviews.review_text: Giving them 5/5 as the owner/staff was incredibly kind, most of the food was great, and price was good. All the food wasn t overly salty or greasy, which is a big plus. We got the double smashed burger, coleslaw, and Cajun chicken plate. Burger was very good, especially liked the sauce. Didn t have the super crispy edges, but was also less greasy. Cheese could ve been melted a bit more, but small nitpicks. Coleslaw was surprisingly my favourite. It was very light and balanced. Slightly tangy, peppery, and just a very nice flavour that was easy to devour. Cajun chicken bowl was alright. It was healthy, and tasted healthy. Nothing too special, thought it could ve used a tad bit more S+P, but personal preference. I m a bit surprised the sun dried tomatoes weren t sliced, as they just put them into the bowl whole. Since they weren t cut, it made them chewier and hard to enjoy as they overpowered every bite. My feedback would be to omit the sun dried tomatoes unless more prep is going into them, as they just detracted from the dish. Overall, everything was delicious and will be back.
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Really appreciate your feedback, Nathan! Well keep working towards that perfect experience! :)

reviews.review_text: I was very pleased with the place, the interior and the overall cleanliness. The folks that work there were very friendly to us. We ordered the fish bites and the fish burger. It was actually pretty good and the fries were very delicious! I noticed in the back the fries seem to be cut fresh so that s a big plus. The garlic aioli was delicious with the fish and went well with the fries! Overall we were very happy with what we got and the price for the food was fair. I would come back for a second try and order the falafel or chicken wraps they offer
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Thank you for sharing your thoughts! Would love to see you again for the falafel! :)

reviews.review_text: I need to edit this review!! After a week of trying this place, I needed to come back and try the Crunchy Garlic Donair that was recommend by the owner. It was so delicious and so fresh and the pita chips inside are the most delicious and crunchiest thing ever. I can t wait to come back again and try something else. Original review!! I ordered the Fish Sandwich with fries and Garlic dip. Everything tastes so good, chips and the fish were so crispy. The place is very clean and has a open view kitchen, so you can see them making your food. I didn t take a picture because it was so good that I forgot! Everyone should try!!! Amazing
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Thank you, Claudia! Yes, transparency is key, as we prepare all meals to order in our open kitchen, so youre welcome to enjoy the show every time! Appreciate the support!

reviews.review_text: Ordered takeout online, it was an easy process. We got the fish sandwich with a cheese bun (never buy a filet o fish again! ) and a crunchy garlic chicken wrap which was sooo packed with flavour. Loved the food here. The space was clean and the staff were pleasant. My only comment is the music was turned up a bit too loud so it was difficult to hear the staff. Edit: tried the falafel--delicious!!
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Thank you for sharing your experience! Wereintroducing summer menu options and would love to see you again! Re music, I admit we do get overexcited at times! Blame it on the loud kitchen equipment! :)

reviews.review_text: This place is Very nice and clean looking and has friendly staff to greet you. They serve Local fish and fresh salad. I tried the fish sandwich and falafel salad both are very tasty and I will be back soon.
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Wonderful!   We look forward to your next visit!

reviews.review_text: Amazing food, fast delivery. The staff is very friendly. Price is good too.   We had fish and chips and Cajun Chicken. Will definitely recommend and go back.
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Thats awesome, thank you! Glad you loved your experience!

reviews.review_text: Stopped by Chef Hyve last night for dinner and ordered their Fish Sandwich made from fresh and sustainable Ling Cod. The sandwich was delicious. It was made fresh when I ordered it - freshly battered in a light coating with their special seasoning and fried. It s nice to be able to enjoy a Fish Sandwich without any worries of cross contamination or having any Haram ingredients to worry about. Also got some of their falafels with crispy pita chips to start with their hummus. They make all their sauces, hummus, coleslaw, salsa in house from fresh high quality ingredients. Also their fries are hand cut in store daily. FYI their Halal Meat supplier is Mediterranean Halal Meats in Vancouver.

We ordered Cheeseburgers and fries. Food is delicious. The only thing I don t like it that is inside is hot, and loud. Cleanliness and food totally deserves 5 stars. Having halal restaurant and it s open till 1 AM.  I will definitely back here but not for dine in, for take out.
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Great news: We got an even bigger AC installed, so now its nice and cool always even when its hot outside! Thank you for the support!

reviews.review_text: Kindest people who clearly take pride in the food they serve. Very refreshing to see nowadays! Food may take a bit of a wait but it is well worth it because everything is made fresh and with love
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Its real food made with love, for sure! :)

reviews.review_text: This place is Definitely   a must try for some comfort food  !!  I ordered the spicy   fish   & chips.. The batter was not too thick ( usually places are stingy with the meat) and was nice & Crispy! The Ice Cream   bar was delicious  . It was dipped in white chocolate   and 3 toppings plus a drizzle of Caramel. And The cheeseburger   was lit  . Check this place out and you will not be disappointed!!!
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Wow, thank you for sharing your thoughts! Reading such feedback makes all the hard work worth it!

reviews.review_text: I love the smell  of food. It s really good. Good atmosphere. Very clean.fast service.  Very friendly.  Taste is yummm

Ive visited chefhyve at least 4 or 5 times. Its always clean and the staff and owner are always very cheerful, friendly and helpful. I tried the fish sandwich, the spicy garlic chicken wrap, the beef burrito, fries as well as ice cream from the ice cream bar and cheese cake. I have to say EVERYTHING tastes greeat, the food is fresh, the restaurant is very clean and the portions are huge even for a big guy like myself. I can never finish the meal! Keep it up Chefhyve, youre raising the bar for restaurants in the lower mainland
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Always lovely to see you! Really appreciate the kind review! Be sure to keep an eye out for new and exciting seasonal menu items! Thank you!!

reviews.review_text: This is my happiest food surprise in 2021 - this is top restaurant quality middle eastern food at 1/2 the price of a place like Nuba. This hole in the wall is not your fast food healthy bowl or typical middle eastern grill. I made the mistake of thinking that as I passed by numerous times and did not go in. I only realized when I saw the chef took out the fresh ingredients and started preparing everything from the beginning in the open kitchen. At first, I was impatient, but then I saw how much care and pride he put in the cooking, and I knew it would be worth it. The pictures cannot capture it because things like hummus and falafel looks similar but taste worlds apart. This may arguably be the best in the city. Even the spicy garlic and tartar sauce was house made and they were so good I kept these for my next meals.
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Wow, appreciate the kind words and detailed review! If you love surprises, then keep an eye out for our spring menus to be rolled out very soon! This might also be the last chance to enjoy some of existing items. Hope to see you again, neighbor :)

reviews.review_text: Chef Hyve is a wonderful restaurant with excellent, friendly service. Their food is Halaal and so tasty! We tried the fish & chips, spicy chicken wrap and their pita chips - all so good! We also had their amazing cheesecake. Highly recommend trying this restaurant.
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Wow, thank you Zaahira! Theres plenty more to try, so keep us in mind the next time youre in the mood for great food! :)

reviews.review_text: Ive gone here a few times now and every time was amazing. I keep meaning to try something different but I keep getting the fish sandwich instead because its sooo good  . Really quite decent prices as well for the quality (OceanWise fish too!) Definitely a return customer !!
reviews.response_from_owner_text: That fish sandwich is addictive, we agree! Speaking of prices, were now running a promo where we serve halibut for the price of cod!! Get yours while quantities last! :)

reviews.review_text: i ordered a wrap and seriously didnt think theyd be able to squeeze all the toppings in, but they did. i was really full after the chili fries are comparable to what youd get at a proper poutine place downtown too. its super loaded
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Much appreciated, Gabriel! Glad you loved our food!

reviews.review_text: We ve been here in person and also had take out a few times - my significant other loves them. Every time the food has been fresh and really thoughtfully made with great flavours :) we re happy they re in our neighbourhood!
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Were grateful to be in this lovely neighbourhood! We wouldnt be here if it werent for all the support the neighbourhood has shown us!

reviews.review_text: Great food, great selection, fresh, and tasty. Staff was very friendly, and efficient. Would come again and recommend.
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Love reading these humbling reviews! Thank you! :)

reviews.review_text: So yummy and filling! I got a fish sandwich for my husband and falafel salad for myself. Both so good!
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Appreciate the support! :)

reviews.review_text: Wow found a gem! As my husband said love at first bite. Awesome tasting food. Fries was awesome taste. Fish burger and burrito was delicious. Finished our meal with Hilda cheesecake. Satisfied and definitely visiting to taste all the other good food in the menu. Clean, bright and big enticing picture menus.
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Many thanks to you and your wonderful family for visiting us! Was a pleasure serving everyone! :)

reviews.review_text: Believe the hype! We had the spicy fish burger with fries and the falafel salad, everything was great. Friendly staff, bright and clean restaurant.
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Appreciate your support, Sara! Would love to serve you again!

reviews.review_text: Having spent quite a while living in the UAE and having had my fair share of great food, I can honestly say that Chefhyve in Vancouver is a real culinary standout. Its one of the best places to eat in the city, and they dont skimp on portion sizes either. What makes Chefhyve truly exceptional is the remarkable flavors they bring to the table. The food is nothing short of delicious, and each bite is a delightful adventure for your taste buds. I have absolutely no hesitation in giving Chefhyve my full recommendation. Its a must-visit spot for anyone looking to savor outstanding food in Vancouver.
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Wow, thats humbling to read! So glad you loved your experience with us! Hope to see you again soon!

reviews.review_text: Was craving a fish sandwich and I ve been wanting to try Chefhyve for a while now and WOW it did not disappoint! The batter is crispy almost like a chicken burger coating. We got the spicy and it was perfect spice for us. The coleslaw was crispy not soggy. We also ordered the Cajun hand cut fries with garlic sauce. So yummy full of flavour I wish we got more garlic sauce! And Alla the owner is so nice and genuine. You can tell he really loves his food and serving the community! Can t wait to go back.. it ll probably become a problem.
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Thank you so much for the detailed review! Hope to see you guys again and wish you all the best in your cafe!

reviews.review_text: My fiance and I decided to give this place a try and take the food to a park nearby. Boy am I ever glad that we did. The burger was so good, I almost went back for another. Too bad I was too full. He got the fish sandwich and it was mind-blowing. Growing up, my dad had a fish and chip restaurant so I am very picky about these things. This place completely exceeded my expectations. Plus the price was incredibly reasonable. Next time, Im coming back for their drizzle ice cream bars because they look insane. I love this place and I will definitely be back.
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Thank you for  taking the time to share your feedback! So glad to see you loved the food!

reviews.review_text: Had the Fish & Chips and the wife had the Fully Loaded Waffle.   Was craving Fish&Chips but the wife wasn t too hungry so we decided where the 2 of us can compromise on both getting what we both want in 1 place.   The Fish&Chips is not your typical English batter style food.  Not greasy and doughy tasting.  Very crisp and not oily at all batter/coating.  The fries are  fresh hand cut kennebec  chips  that are also very tasty and not oily tasting at all.  The dessert waffle was also nice and sweet. But not too sweet either that makes it very enjoyable.  I don t have photos of before eating except for the end results. (Sorry).  Ps .. Fish&Chips seem to be very popular dish as 5 ppl did takeout while we were eating there.
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Well those empty plates tell the whole story, dont they! Would love to see you again soon!

reviews.review_text: Came here during the day on a Saturday, no lines! Had the full place to ourselves. The Falafel Salad and Crunchy Chicken Wrap were amazing!! The ice cream bars were delicious too and an experience to watch them do it. You can tell the owner and staff care about the business and its patrons. Probably the best we have had in the city and the price is fair for the amount of food you get. Theres free parking on the street as well. Will be back for more.
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Thank you for sharing your experience! Would love to see you again for sure!

reviews.review_text: This spot has been here about a year. Stopped in to try their Fish and Chips. Got a 1 piece Ling cod dinner . It was tasty with a nice light batter. You can choice from Original, Mildly Spiced or Hot. Also got a side of Carrit Humuus that was tasty, too
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Thanks for sharing! Hope to see you again! :)

reviews.review_text: This place had alot of options. I like everything Ive ate here. My two favorites are the crunchy garlic chicken wrap and the chicken burrito.
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Thank you for the support, Greg! :) And thank you for recommending us to so many friends and family. We truly appreciate it!

reviews.review_text: The only place like it in the neighbourhood! Ala, is warm, friendly and kind. The food is fresh and made to order. I m definitely ordering from them again!
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Thank you, James! You are too kind!

reviews.review_text: I was in the area doing my laundry, needed some time to kill and wanted some good healthy food. A local suggested i try Chefhyve..,I was not disappointed lovingly made super delicious food. Everything in this is made by them no processes food at all and it showed, they even cook the falafel only when you order it. This guy is a genius and his philosophy is just like that off a high end chef   cant recommend the food enough will be going back again and again   thank you. !
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Thank you! Yes, we offer real food, made in small batches in house using fresh, local ingredients. The homemade falafel is no exception, and well continue to be making it to order each and every time. Would love to see you again for more vegan + vegetarian goodness! :)

reviews.review_text: Amazing spot for wraps, burgers and ice cream! Had the crunchy garlic chicken wrap. All ingredients were fresh and tasty. Service was excellent!
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Thanks for sharing your experience!

reviews.review_text: Very tasty and delicious food. Service was great, chef prepared the food with heart, very professionally and was very hospitable. We were visiting from Toronto/GTA where there are lots of halal food places, this place with the amazing environment and amazing menu exceeded our expectations. Best food we had in a while, definitely recommend
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Thank you for your visit and recommendation! Safe trip back! :)

reviews.review_text: Nice place for a quick meal or takeout. I recommend the fish sandwich and fish bites. They are both delicious and come in a good portion!
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Thanks for sharing your experience! Much appreciated! Hope to see you again! :)

reviews.review_text: If you want to experience food that is artistically made, flavourful, and top notch service then this is the spot. The food is on point, and healthy. Keep up the great service and work Chef!
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Always a pleasure having you with us! Looking fwd to your next visit! :) Respect!

reviews.review_text: Like the guy eating at the table said when we walked in, this food is delicious. Delicious, delicious, delicious. Friendly staff, friendly customers and friendly atmosphere. Will definitely be back.
reviews.response_from_owner_text: So glad youve enjoyed your experience! We make sure it remains consistently impressive! Thank you!

reviews.review_text: We really like the care the Chef at this restaurant puts into how he prepares his food.  I have tried several dishes & each one was excellent.  The latest new item we tried was the Chili Fries, delicious!
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Appreciate your continued support, Gloria! Hope to continue winning your approval! :)

reviews.review_text: We got there before it got busy. Nice atmosphere and good food. The employee/chef was really nice and helpful!
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Appreciate the support! Hope to see you again! :)

reviews.review_text: i came here on my families recommendation and genuinely the best food i ve ever ordered, i got the veggie fries and single burger and i will definitely be coming back Food
reviews.response_from_owner_text: So glad you loved it! :)

reviews.review_text: Every once in a while, if you have any luck, you may find a gem in the ocean of gravel. I happened upon chefhyve, a few days back, and was feeling lucky that I had. Mediocrity has become normalized, so when you find an exceptional establishment, you may want to share the love. It is more than evident that Ala takes great pride in his work, his team and their offerings. This level of food business may seem a little out of place, considering the surroundings, but that just adds to its charm. This menu has literally something for everyone and, no matter what you order, you will not be disappointed. Top props to Ala and his team. Everything about chefhyve is a reflection of the management and the consideration they have for their customers. Well done, yall.
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Thanks, Professor! It was our pleasure having you dine with us. Your kind words and encouragement are sincerely appreciated. Really look forward to seeing you again soon!

reviews.review_text: We went here for ice cream bars & it exceeded my expectations. You get to choose a sauce to dip your ice cream bar in + 3 toppings & another sauce as a drizzle.  Very delicious & reasonably priced. They also have a variety of sandwiches all of which sounded great.  Ill be back for lunch one day
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Thank you so much for the honest review! Hope to see you next time for lunch!

reviews.review_text: Good food, flavorful, lots of veggie options, simply AMAZING!! Enjoyed to the max, definitely a 10/10. Clean and very well maintained place. The owner was very welcoming, service 10/10. A MUST TRY!!!
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Thank you so much for the kind words and positive review. They help a great deal for our small, local business.

reviews.review_text: I stopped eating midway just to write this. Its incredible. Ill be coming back as much as I can. Youre missing out if you dont eat here. I didnt catch the name of the person working behind the counter but he was really nice. Edit: just found out the cooks/chefs get rotated every day - who made the food on Jun 28, 2021??
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Hi friend! We sincerely appreciate your support and feedback. Ala was helping you that day and carefully preparing your food. Were so glad you enjoyed the experience here and hope to see you here often!

reviews.review_text: We ordered take out tonight and it was so delicious! We tried the falafel and lamb plates.  Everything was so fresh and had so much flavour.  The spicy feta and hummus were our faves.  Would highly recommend!
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Thank you so much, Sandra, for sharing your experience with us!

reviews.review_text: This place is a hidden gem that opened late last year in 2020.  As I have been here a few times already, on this day I sampled the grilled chicken and it did not disappoint.  It should be noted that everything here is made fresh and that is one of the main reasons the food has very good taste.  Check it out....
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Its always great to see you again, Ronald! Glad you loved our food :) See you soon!

reviews.review_text: I found myself as a pretty criticizing person. I didn t have any expectation for the foods from here cuz it s kinda fast food. But once I tried it, I know that this is a real. I can feel that the cook knows definitely what s/he is doing. Can t wait to order other food again!
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Thank you, Claire! Would love to serve you again, for sure!

reviews.review_text: Ok I never really leave reviews unless it s really bad or really good and this was sooooo good. Ordered through doordash, took about 35min to get my food. Ordered 1pc fish and fries, double cheeseburger and crunchy garlic chicken wrap. The fish wasn t as crunchy by the time it got here but it definitely wasn t soggy and was still so delicious, can t imagine what it would be fresh. The wrap was delicious, it was different. So tasty. I love smash burgers but so far from where I am and this was as close to that. So delicious, my husband and I really enjoyed everything! Can t wait to order again or try it fresh!
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Appreciate the support! Enjoying it in person is even better! :)

reviews.review_text: Good food. Decent price. Very motivated chef. You can tell he loves what he does. Great service. Friendly atmosphere.
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Appreciate the support!!

reviews.review_text: The menu is surprisingly extensive and I cant wait to try everything this place has to offer! They courageously prep all their food in front of their customers and manage to keep their cooking area immaculate. I had the garlic chicken wrap which was sufficiently garlicky with a nice mysterious crunch inside which I looked forward to with every bite. My wife had the In and Out inspired cheeseburger which was juicy and deliciously messy. Everyone there was genuinely passionate about the food they were serving and made us feel like regulars despite us visiting for the very first time. Cant wait to go back!
reviews.response_from_owner_text: The menu is addictive, so we hope to see you become regulars! Appreciate the feedback!

reviews.review_text: I walked in & asked what was recommended. Two customers called from behind me Fish Sandwich!!. I tried it & agree - its really something to shout about. Recommend.
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Thank you!! Hope to see you again! :)

reviews.review_text: Wether it s for a healthy lunch, or a late night snack, Chef Hyve Rocks! The staff are always friendly and the food is the best in the area. Would highly recommend!
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Appreciate the support, neighbour! Always a pleasure to serve you!

reviews.review_text: Love at first bite. I am a hardcore food critic, and if I could give 50 stars they would definitely have them. Clean. Bright. Exceptional attitude and professional courtesy with local supply for their original menu ideas and comforting decore in a compact venue. You wont be disappointed. The Beef burrito is to die for.
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Yessss 50 stars, please!!! :))) You guys were awesome. We immensely enjoyed our conversation as well! Thank you for supporting your neighborhood restaurant! We hope to keep seeing your lovely family :)

reviews.review_text: Not exaggerating when I say the food was amazing. The food placement, the food, the quality of the ingredients, the portions and the owner, super friendly guy. You cant go wrong here, I would definitely recommend it.
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Thank you so much for sharing your thoughts and for the support! Hopefully youll return soon to experience our winter menu and dessert bar!

reviews.review_text: Excellent food! The owner was very helpful to decide what to get as it was our first time here. We tried the Crunchy garlic chicken wrap - comes in a pita that was very filling for a single sitting. Husband got the Cajun Chicken plate which came with more greens. The place is clean, not crazy busy and the food leaves you feeling satisfied. Small place on Kingsway but we will definitely be back again!
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Appreciate the support! Was lovely serving you today! Remember, no experience is complete without the desserts! Come back for round 2!

reviews.review_text: Holy!!! So good!! If you like spicy food ask the chef to add extra and the wraps will blow your mind!
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Thank you for joining us today with the lovely family!

reviews.review_text: I ordered the fish sandwich and the fish and chips from here and they were fantastic! Everything was fresh and delicious. There was a wait for the food which was a little annoying but the food was well worth the wait. I ve also gotten their ice cream which was very yummy as well. So many dips and toppings. The staff is very nice too.
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Yes, we only do fresh ingredients, including all the fish! :) You may also order ahead on our website to save time as we prepare all meals to order! Thanks again! :)

reviews.review_text: First try of this place in our neighborhood.  Delicious!  The fish was cooked to perfection with quality ling cod, flaky and glistening in a crunchy batter.  So good and lots of food for the money. The chicken garlic wrap is fresh and delicious, also made with crunch and fresh veggies, warning this thing is huge and food enough for two. The Chef is very friendly and enthusiastic.  Cant wait to try the desserts. Well be going back soon!
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Awesome, glad you guys loved our food! Hope to see you soon for a decadent treat! :)

reviews.review_text: Ordered the beef burrito. Crispy on the outside, tender on the inside, and packed with flavour.
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Sounds about right! Appreciate your support of our small, local restaurant! :)

reviews.review_text: Absolute top notch service, world class food, and extremely clean! Would absolutely recommend!!! Enjoyed the interaction as much as I enjoyed the food
reviews.response_from_owner_text: And world class customers! :) Thank you, Abdullah, for your kind words and support! Weve enjoyed your visit just as much and sincerely hope youd choose us again the next time youre in the mood for great food and great service! Thanks again!

reviews.review_text: Got fish bites with fries and a cheesecake, it was super delicious and fresh. I ll be going back to try more!
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Thanks for sharing your experience!

reviews.review_text: Very clean, high quality food
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Thank you for the support! :)

reviews.review_text: We ve been here twice now and it s still delicious! Amazing hidden gem on Kingsway :)) Fish and chips are the best with mild spice and the cheesecake is heavenly. Ice cream is super fancy with all the toppings and very sweet. I need to come back soon!
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Love the support! Thank you!

reviews.review_text: It was amazing their burrito, and fish burger.  Next time I will try more dishes.
reviews.response_from_owner_text: For sure, theres plenty more great dishes to keep you coming back! :))

reviews.review_text: Good seasoning and portion size. Always a satisfying meal here
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Thank you for the support!

reviews.review_text: Very good fish burger! The fries were surprisingly good too! Food
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Love the support! :)

reviews.review_text: Just picked up lunch from here today for the first time. I tried the fish and chips and the crunchy garlic chicken wrap. I dont normally post reviews but it was so good I thought I should. I like how ingredients are high quality and fresh. Everything tasted great! Ill be visiting on a regular basis to support them.
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Wow, thank you for the support! Hope to keep seeing you! :)

reviews.review_text: Delicious chicken & lamb platters Excellent concept and very pleased with the dedication to the experience. Worth the drive down Kingsway and looking forward to our next meal from here.
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Super glad youve enjoyed your meals! Thanks for dropping by and for your understanding re out of stock items :)

reviews.review_text: Had our first visit yesterday! I tried crunchy chicken wrap and fish bites with fries. They are soooo delicious and fresh!!! I love how they are made unique and original yet very authentic :)! Will definitely come back !!!
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Its food made with love! :) Appreciate the support!

reviews.review_text: First time here came with a freind, wowwwwwwww is all I have to say I had the spicy chicken wrap and it was super flavourful!!! One of the best chicken wraps iv ever had the chicken quality and hummus plus all the veg was outta This world. Took home the lotus biscotti cheese cake and that was unreal too!!! Highly recommend this gem!
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Thanks, brother! Your genuine support means so much to our team!

reviews.review_text: Finally got to give this a try ! Driven by many times with the intention to try it out. Today was the day, glad I did. Cajun Chicken Bowl was a great experience. Distinct flavours with additions that were surprising to find. A Fresh and healthy choice!
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Glad you finally made it! The other items are just a great and bursting with flavour, promise!

reviews.review_text: We ordered fish & chips and chicken burrito,both were delicious and not your usual fish & chips and chicken burrito at all. It s nice to have this kind of place 1 minute away from our place. Staff were nice and friendly and the place is clean and tidy. BYO ice cream bar is also a must try!
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Thank you,  neighbor!  Hope to provide you with a great experience time and again! :)

reviews.review_text: This gem of a place is near me and I stop in for their falafel salad which is absolutely delicious! Everything is prepared fresh and they make their falafels to order. Nothing frozen or microwaved and nothing from packages. And their ice cream bars are on a different level. Highly recommend checking this place out! But be forewarned, once you eat here you will quickly become addicted :)
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Wow, appreciate the kind words and humbling feedback! Thank you :)

reviews.review_text: Delicious food for reasonable price. Definitely coming back!
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Thank you, wed love to see you again! :)

reviews.review_text: Quality food we got the wamba lamb, the buck buck bowl and Iced Tea every thing is made from scratch....great price point amazing quality
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Thank you for coming to see us! Hope to see you soon!

reviews.review_text: Wow this place was delicious! A breathe of fresh air to great food in the area and a newer restaurant in the neighborhood! I ve lived in the area for over thirty years and have yet to come across a good restaurant like this! The fish sandwich I ordered was mouth watering delicious! The ice cream was 5 stars too! I usually never write reviews unless they are really good or terrible, so for me to write something speaks a lot.  The prices were really good too. I ll definitely be back!
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Wow! We are humbled by such reviews! So grateful for the love this community has shown us! We promise to maintain the quality and taste that you love! Hope to see you again soon!

reviews.review_text: By far my favourite place in the area. Unbelievably tasty and such friendly service. I ve tried almost everything on the menu and enjoyed each item, but the warm plates are 11/10 in flavour. Big fan of the fish bites, street burrito and cheesecake
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Thank you for the continued support and kind review!

reviews.review_text: Had a fish sandwich and it was great. I m happy that There is a good restaurant in the neighborhood
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Thank you for sharing!

reviews.review_text: Outstanding flavor, clean and personal service. Gordon Ramsay would be impressed. All the food we have tasted is extremely good. There is a wait BECAUSE it is all made fresh. Fish and chips are not frozen so get them when they are available, chicken so fresh and juicy cant stop eating. The fries are from fresh potatoes, not frozen like the rest of the food, so quantity is limited get it or come back next time. The owner is also an absolute ray of sunshine. Hes kind, friendly, and wants to give the best product and service, and he suceeds! Your doing a fantastic job!
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Wow, you are too kind! Such a humbling review. Well remain committed to serving real food with a big smile! This community has been so supportive, its amazing! Also, waffles, chicken soup and new burritos and salads are literally days away in the fall menu! Hope to see you soon! :)

reviews.review_text: Fantastic place on Kingsway with delicious fresh Middle Eastern-inspired food & much more. Super clean, bright & friendly vibe, and especially fantastic service by the server Fatima, who was very helpful, knowledgeable and delightful. Will come back again for sure!
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Were grateful for your visit and feedback, Daniel. Thanks!
